Yes — and you should.

Otherwise after session expiry Arthur Core won’t know which application login flow to restart.

Best approach:

```text
/sales-points?appId=B2BOOST_BE
```

and on expiry:

```text
/auth/start?appId=B2BOOST_BE
```

