# Recommended implementation

## 1. Add `appId` param to sales-points URL

After callback:

Instead of:

```java
response.sendRedirect("/arthur-core/sales-points");
```

use:

```java
response.sendRedirect(
        "/arthur-core/sales-points?appId=" + URLEncoder.encode(tx.getAppId(), StandardCharsets.UTF_8)
);
```

---

# 2. Update controller

## GET `/sales-points`

```java
@GetMapping
public ModelAndView salesPoints(
        @RequestParam String appId,
        @CookieValue(value = "ARTHUR_SESSION", required = false) String sessionId
) {

    if (sessionId == null || sessionId.isBlank()) {
        return new ModelAndView("redirect:/auth/start?appId=" + appId);
    }

    UserSession session = redisSessionService.findBySessionId(sessionId);

    if (session == null) {
        return new ModelAndView("redirect:/auth/start?appId=" + appId);
    }

    ModelAndView mv = new ModelAndView("views/sales-points");
    mv.addObject("salesPoints", session.getSalesPoints());
    mv.addObject("appId", appId);

    return mv;
}
```

