# 3. Update POST `/select`

```java
@PostMapping("/select")
public void selectSalesPoint(
        @RequestParam String appId,
        @CookieValue(value = "ARTHUR_SESSION", required = false) String sessionId,
        @RequestParam String salesPointId,
        HttpServletResponse response
) throws IOException {

    if (sessionId == null || sessionId.isBlank()) {
        response.sendRedirect("/arthur-core/auth/start?appId=" + appId);
        return;
    }

    String redirectUrl =
            authService.completeSalesPointSelection(sessionId, salesPointId);

    response.sendRedirect(redirectUrl);
}
```

