# 4. Thymeleaf form

Add hidden appId field:

```html
<input type="hidden" name="appId" th:value="${appId}">
```

Final form:

```html
<form method="post" th:action="@{/sales-points/select}">

    <input type="hidden" name="appId" th:value="${appId}">

    <div th:each="sp : ${salesPoints}">
        <label>
            <input type="radio"
                   name="salesPointId"
                   th:value="${sp.id}"
                   required>

            <span th:text="${sp.label}">Sales Point</span>
        </label>
        <br>
    </div>

    <button type="submit">Confirm</button>
</form>
```

